sub_title: Co-Owner Young Engineers Vračar Beograd and Jack's Hands-on English Belgrade
summary:
Hello, I'm a visionary poet, artist, philosopher - with lots of hands-on, practical experience as a software engineer, Permaculturist and teacher (IBDP, European Baccalaureate, Community College and European secondary education). I am now in Belgrade with my Serbian fiancée with whom we are starting up a Young Engineers franchise in Vračar (Belgrade) https://vracar.beograd.youngengineers.org/ and an English teaching-coaching company: Jack's Hands-on English Belgrade www.handsonbelgrade.org .

My ultimate goal is to encourage kids to create a new reality and to manifest my Vision for a new dynamic school system ... The Virtue School http://virtueschool.org
